Package com.evite.qv.model

Class Summary
QVAd QVAd contains the ad img src and click url for rendering an ad on the target device.
QVAdInputData QVAdInputData should contain as much data as possible necessary to render an ad.
QVContact QVContact represents a simplified version of our ContactObject.
QVCredentials QVCredentials contains the web service API client's credentials to indentify them.
QVDate QVDate represents a simple date (minus timezone, etc) to be used with the QV interface
QVEvent QVEvent represents a simplified version of the EventsObject for use with the QVWebService.
QVEventDecorator QVEventWithGuestlist simply contains an event, guest list, response summary
QVGroup QVGroup represents a group of users.
QVGroupWithContacts QVGroupWithContacts simply holds the QVGroup and it's associated contact list
QVInvite QVInvite represents a simplified version of the InvitesObject to be used with the QVWebService API.
QVInviteDecorator QVInviteDecorator simply holds an invite and some of the information for the event associated with it.
QVPhoto QVPhoto contains event/owner information for the photo as well as a link to the image on the Evite site.
QVSmsOptIn QVSmsOptIn keeps track of the status of the SMS opt-in for a qv user.
P (pending) then they have not responded yet.
O (opted out) then they do not want to receive sms messages from us.
I (opted in) then they have opted in and want to receive
QVUserProfile QVProfile represents a user's profile information (this is one per user, not to be confused with QVContact, which is a particular user's addressbook entry for what may or may not be another user).

QVSmsOptIn.Status  
QVWebServiceException.ErrorCode ErrorCode is the machine-parsable code for the exception AUTH_ERROR = authentication error (incorrect QVCredentials) MISSING_REQUIRED_DATA = the data in the request was missing required fields (error message will elaborate) DATA_INVALID = the data in the request contained invalid fields (error message will elaborate) NOT_VERIFIED = the sender's mobile number has not been verified APP_FAULT = application error on our side (io, db, etc)
 

Exception Summary
QVWebServiceException QVWebserviceException represents an exception for the QV webservice :)
